{"id": 2253, "genre": 1001, "title": "自从养了宠物，你的人生都发生过哪些变化？", "description": "为了“迁就”它们，你都（被迫）做出过哪些牺牲？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2864, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180329160808gTzXq29V3GCsuf0F.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-02T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 273920, "content": "生活健康了，宅家爱好者现在起码会每天都得出门溜一趟狗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798705}, {"id": 273921, "content": "每次放假第一时间赶回家，\n从爱逛淘宝变成爱逛宠物网", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302314}, {"id": 273922, "content": "每天下班再也不敢慢悠悠，想早点回家看到狗子，给他喂食。", "image": "img/option/option/201804022135158Un031PrBEAC5Ysd.jpg", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302328}, {"id": 273923, "content": "曾经养过狗狗，小学的时候，尤其暑假，家里的时光都是和它呆在一起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302335}, {"id": 273924, "content": "每件大衣都变毛衣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265413}, {"id": 273925, "content": "遛狗，铲屎是每天的日常。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 390893}, {"id": 273926, "content": "出远门第三天就开始想他，想早点结束行程把他从寄养的地方解救出来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 271227}, {"id": 273927, "content": "转行宠物业?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230760}, {"id": 273929, "content": "以前的我不叠被子，不铺床罩，不擦桌子，不扫地，不开窗，不洗杯子，不洗床单", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122485}, {"id": 273931, "content": "金毛很好养，每年只掉两次毛，每次掉半年", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597684}, {"id": 273932, "content": "我养了三条鱼，以后夜不归宿的活动不要叫我，因为我晚上要喂鱼", "image": "img/option/option/20180402231246dw3n5gOrhQmiEbCY", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124597}, {"id": 274444, "content": "因为养的猛犬，溜狗怕吓到老人小孩，所以每天晚睡早起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304912}, {"id": 274956, "content": "变得喜欢擦地，吸毛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688564}, {"id": 273933, "content": "每次厕所洗完澡都要关门以防狗尿垫上", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279910}, {"id": 273934, "content": "不敢长途旅行了，不放心别人照顾自己的猫，不欢迎朋友来家里，怕猫被吓到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672255}, {"id": 273935, "content": "影响我的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293117}, {"id": 273936, "content": "我的猫刚来我家不习惯水晶猫砂，在床上拉屎拉尿时，我都是轻手轻脚把它抱开然后洗棉被到凌晨两点，可是我的一一还是超乖超可爱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844329}, {"id": 273937, "content": "我猫的照片被我设成桌面，工作不顺心时就看看它毛茸茸的，心情一下子就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844329}, {"id": 273938, "content": "想养又不敢养", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302399}, {"id": 277267, "content": "铲屎官真累……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275677}, {"id": 273940, "content": "狗遛人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930971}, {"id": 274453, "content": "想去哪，首先担心它的伙食问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288287}, {"id": 273942, "content": "宿舍养了猫，从此衣柜外再也没有出现过衣服?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296780}, {"id": 273943, "content": "这个酸奶真好喝，我家狗肯定爱喝，不行我要给它留着", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748059}, {"id": 274455, "content": "不孤单了，还有更喜欢小动物了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304910}, {"id": 273944, "content": "每天都要回家想着喂他", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271213}, {"id": 273945, "content": "不再孤单", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300535}, {"id": 275737, "content": "定期清理手机照片，啥都可以删，狗的不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315073}, {"id": 273946, "content": "桌上比我脸还干净（大哥会叼走一切她能叼走的东西然后粉碎性破坏）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302450}, {"id": 273947, "content": "养養了貓之後，我學會了做飯，我在桌上吃饭，它在桌下吃飯??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295414}, {"id": 273948, "content": "學會了茶言悦色", "image": "img/option/option/20180403024300MWtbIBjFc64ogE7P.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295414}, {"id": 274460, "content": "整颗心都变得柔软起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305112}, {"id": 273950, "content": "被迫？不存在的，我是主动的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878479}, {"id": 275998, "content": "治愈了我的宅，每天遛狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159310}, {"id": 273952, "content": "没事会学狼叫逗狗（人比狗叫的多）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204898}, {"id": 277280, "content": "没想到世界还能如此美好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112037}, {"id": 273953, "content": "因为夏天狗狗掉毛，每到夏天鼻子就会特别难受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302509}, {"id": 273954, "content": "周五放学撸猫心急，公车不倒坐出租", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016791}, {"id": 273955, "content": "毛毛毛，翔翔翔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 108007}, {"id": 274211, "content": "该说的都说了，我还能说啥…………", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256282}, {"id": 273956, "content": "更温暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302518}, {"id": 273957, "content": "每天面对猫毛、猫屎、沙发窗帘床单被猫抓的孔、易碎品统统装起来、桌子上没有杯子（如果有一定会被舔）、睡眠不足（每天早上五点准时开始挠门）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302519}, {"id": 274469, "content": "对称赞猫猫的客人特别热情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850332}, {"id": 273958, "content": "有猫有狗\n还要什么女朋友\n哼哼～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206638}, {"id": 274470, "content": "不想看着它死去ಥ_ಥ", "image": "img/option/option/20180406162126sxwBAKWey0i9PUFO", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305221}, {"id": 281638, "content": "手机里面都是他的照片\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344147}, {"id": 273959, "content": "上厕所，有狗看门了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301764}, {"id": 277287, "content": "不能带他们一起那就不出去旅游，人民币可着他们先花，早起遛狗打扫卫生，捡屎铲屎动作利落?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324279}, {"id": 288807, "content": "有狗就是全世界，把所有的耐心都给了我们家狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 273960, "content": "经常风言风语，对狗说一些我都听不懂的话╮(╯▽╰)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753458}]}